cooldown reduction per enemy hit 0.20 0.30 0.40 0.50 second
debuff duration 3.2 3.8 4.4 5
cooldown 16
mana cost 70 110 150 190 plus 3% of max mana

talent level 10 Upgrade Thunder Clap
increase strenght scaling by 15%
increase radius by 70
increase attack speed lost by 10
increase movement speed lost by 8%
increase bonus damage per enemy by 3

add a new mofidier Hammer of Thunder
Enemys hit by Thunder Clap will have 50% chance to get lightning Bolt dealing 25 30 35 40 plus 80% of Thordin Strenght in pure damage
and enemys that are below 40% will lose 3% of their Max health 0.4% for bosses and any enemys that die from the Lightning Bolt will
Heal Thordin by 4% of his max health and every Unit hit by Thunder Clap will restore Thordin health by 25% of the damage done with
Thunder Clap

SPELL E
Strenght of the Mountain
Thordin next attack will deal bonus damage and increase attack speed as well, The last hit will deal triple the damage and do cleave
attack. this spell Cannot crit from any other source but Avatar

damage bonus 8 12 16 20 Physical
attack speed bonus 35
number of attack 3
last hit damage increase 24 36 48 60 Physical
last hit cleave damage 25% 50% 75% 100%
radius of cleave 370 390 410 430 in front of Thordin
no mana cost
cooldown 38 32 26 20

talent level 15 upgrade Strenght of the Mountain
increase damage by 4
increase attack speed by 35
increase last hit damage by 12
increase cleave radius by 100

add a new modifier Lightning Zone
after landing the last hit create a lightning zone of 600 radius that deal 8 magical damage plus 15% of Thordin strenght to nearby enemy
and for ally and Thordin, they gain 20% increase base damage and 12% spell amp while inside of it the zone last 10 second and after the
Lightning Zone is gone, it will restore all allys and Thordin health by 5% plus 1% for every hero allys while inside of Lightning Zone
when its gone

